text: Cheng Te-mei () is a general officer of the Republic of China Army (ROCA) in Taiwan. He was the Vice Minister (Armaments) of National Defense, having served in this capacity from 1 November 2015 to 28 April 2017. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Republic of China Army Category:Military personnel of the Republic of China Category:1955 births
title: Cheng Te-mei
